org.hibernate.search.query.dsl.sort.impl

Class SortFieldStates

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.search.query.dsl.sort.impl.SortFieldStates

  • public class SortFieldStates
extends Object
    Holds the list of @{link SortField}s as well as the state of the one being constructed. Use closeSortField() to add the current SortField to the list of created sort fields. Use createSort() to return Lucene's sort object.
    Author:
    Emmanuel Bernard emmanuel@hibernate.org
